{"tid":353780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC:搖滾樂如何推動了共產黨政權的垮台？","createTime":"2017-08-10T01:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T11:03:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"449b6721fd0e67f9507ab7266c2e9ecea86bb080","tid":353780,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:53:34.000Z","msg":"........東德當局這樣的重拳旨在阻止年輕人跟著西方&quot;帝國主義&quot;的音樂轉。但是，對西方音樂的熱愛不僅與日俱增，而且逐漸進入遠離大城市的鄉下。<br />\n<br />\n東德少年亞歷山大&middot;庫納（Alexander Kuehne）家在距離柏林好幾小時車程的偏遠小村，迫切希望能聽到更多的音樂.....<br />\n<br />\n.......庫納決定把家鄉小村打造成有名的音樂場所。小村恰好離一個主要的鐵路樞紐不遠，他說服各種各樣的音樂迷、樂隊來小村酒吧後的一個房間聚會。<br />\n<br />\n他帶我參觀，邊走邊說，&quot;就是在這裏，我們搞過東德最大的派對。&quot;酒吧裏的農夫有時看到很好笑，大批流行音樂粉絲從身邊走過、義無反顧地去後面的房間。庫納說，最多時來的人達到過1000。警方規定的那個房間的最大容量是100人。<br />\n<br />\n小村山高皇帝遠，警察和斯塔西慢慢兒才醒過味兒來，開始採取行動對付這種大型聚會。有一次，庫納被抓起來帶到警察局，警察說斯塔西轉天要找他談談，他說，&quot;我很害怕。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n還好，他的媽媽原來教過當地的警察。媽媽下令警察放了自己的孩子，然後又搞定了登門的斯塔西。她從來沒有告訴孩子具體內幕。時至今日，庫納回憶往事對媽媽仍是充滿敬意，&quot;她是我的英雄。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但是在大城市，斯塔西對那些&quot;顛覆性&quot;、&quot;反社會&quot;的音樂迷的嚴打一如既往.....<br />\n<br />\n怎麼理解朋克這類人呢？檔案顯示，梅爾克曾經絞盡腦汁，試圖搞懂朋克、重金屬這些奇怪的概念。<br />\n<br />\n我找到了尤爾根&middot;布雷斯基（Jurgen Breski），當時的斯塔西官員，曾奉命滲透朋克圈兒。他同意和我在市中心一家餐館的隱秘一角見面，向我講述了當年上司給他的指令。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;他們要讓人們過一種社會主義的生活方式，所以我們就想辦法打擊那些不屬於社會主義生活方式的東西。目的是要控制'局面'，阻止它廣泛流傳。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n最後，斯塔西還是用的老辦法：盡可能多地發展告密者。其他一些措施還包括，把非法樂隊的成員叫去服兵役、派到外地去，布雷斯基說，&quot;突然，樂隊沒有樂手了！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但是，很多人依然決心&quot;頂風作案&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朋克樂隊Zerfall(崩潰)的德爾克&middot;卡林諾夫斯基（Dirk Kalinowski）告訴我，斯塔西向他本人、他的樂隊施加巨大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n他們能夠堅持下去，一個難以置信的主要原因是，柏林一家教堂成了他們的舞台和庇護所。東德當局儘管在許多事上鐵血無情，但是並不希望直接干涉教會招來國際社會的關注。<br />\n<br />\n卡林諾夫斯基的樂隊被禁止參加正常演出，但是，他們可以在教會禱告過程中演唱。牧師會暫停&hellip;&hellip;然後讓一群上了年紀的信徒聽點兒不同聲音。<br />\n<br />\n卡林諾夫斯基回憶，&quot;瘋了一樣。我是主唱，可以直接看到人群，他們震驚的面孔。不在乎的只有孩子，聽到音樂立刻亂蹦亂跳。我永遠不會忘記，一對老夫婦堵著耳朵走出教堂。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n還有一家教堂成為另外一場不尋常的音樂會的舞台。英國音樂製作人馬克&middot;里德（Mark Reed）將西德一個朋克樂隊「死褲子」（Die Toten Hosen）偷偷帶過柏林牆演出。里德回憶，當時他對東德人說，我被抓住了，最多被趕出國；你被抓住了，一生可能就完了，你會被看作公敵，<br />\n<br />\n他們回答，「不在乎，就是想這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-40813492\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-40813492&d=G6m4a0XYGbAzLntwRX7pqNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e4388ea8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-40813492&h=2a7b44b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-40813492</a>"},{"pid":"2095f22bc496a84b03ff06a6e9a0595ed24fe114","tid":353780,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:55:17.000Z","msg":".....可以搬出各種各樣的禁令，但是，音樂粉絲想方設法創造自由空間，這成了東歐共產黨執政國家的特有現象。<br />\n<br />\n1980年代中期開始，莫斯科的新領導人戈爾巴喬夫放鬆了對東德的鐵腕控制。<br />\n<br />\n柏林牆邊，西方音樂的音量越來越大。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1987年，大名鼎鼎的大衛&middot;鮑伊（David Bowie）在緊靠柏林牆西邊的地方舉行演唱會，東德粉絲聚在牆邊大飽耳福。<br />\n<br />\n當時東柏林的副警監迪特爾&middot;迪茨（Dieter Dietze）還比較年輕，這事讓他很為難。他知道，如果警察像1969年（滾石樂隊謠傳要來的時候）那樣出重拳壓制的話，肯定會起到反作用。他本人也是搖滾粉絲，還曾是樂隊成員，他告訴我，他很同情年輕的音樂迷。<br />\n<br />\n不過，東德領導人還是最看重穩定、秩序。<br />\n<br />\n迪茨說，&quot;我很清楚，音樂--搖滾音樂--屬於年輕人，你根本擋不住。所以，我和其它幾個人開始討論，為什麼我們不也搞這樣的活動？&quot;</strong><br />\n<br />\n後來，東德當局批准世界級超級明星在東德土地開演唱會，這包括鮑勃&middot;迪倫（Bob Dylan）和布魯斯&middot;斯普林斯廷（Bruce Springsteen）。當局本想拿這個當安全閥，給年輕人減減壓、取悅拉攏一下。但是，音樂會反倒加強了年輕人對自由的嚮往。<br />\n<br />\n霍夫斯塔德說，斯普林斯廷那類音樂會&quot;成了要求人權、自由表述、對外面世界渴望的焦點體現。<br />\n<br />\n想像一下，10萬東德年輕人齊聲高唱'生於美國'！&quot;"},{"pid":"80b83e6ae6d48e3b45761bbd82cb3b6a31656df5","tid":353780,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"1960年代，滾石樂隊粉絲想聽聽心中的偶像，要冒著坐牢的危險，&quot;到了80年代，他們不再害怕了，當局失去了控制。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n冷戰的結束有許多原因，政治的、經濟的，但是，對自由的嚮往也很重要。1989年，這種嚮往激勵成千上萬的東德人走上街頭、衝向柏林牆，挑戰共產主義當局。對於很多人來說，音樂支撐著、體現著他們的嚮往。<br />\n<br />\n水泥牆、機關槍、鐵絲網可以擋住人，但是擋不住音樂。<br />\n<br />\n霍夫斯塔德說，&quot;音樂進入你的大腦、心靈，你一定會聽。&quot;在她看來，那一切，都可以歸結於一句古老的德國諺語：<br />\n<br />\n思想是自由的。"},{"pid":"21e9f893cd31232d7329dbe400d9a0b39dd9840f","tid":353780,"uid":46644,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cbee70fb3160ef2088f396307b1b70ff61697df","tid":353780,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪係，去玩音樂好過搞革命被人拉到坐牢咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題音樂都唔俾玩<br />\n<br />\nHa事件"},{"pid":"da4c567a094fd9d41da6e8338cb827dd64b9bfb4","tid":353780,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:18:06.000Z","msg":"但係亞洲區尤其係華人社會一定行唔通<br />\n畜牲係唔識音樂，只識食扑野訓"},{"pid":"53fb14bd6aa01da4d5e9c4780cb642e5757257eb","tid":353780,"uid":19113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:29:36.000Z","msg":"只有兩個下場，一係就為政治服務，唔係就被封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223924c86a5a3414b65dbb59ac17660743beecc1","tid":353780,"uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"音樂係要有靈性，有思想既動物先聽得明"},{"pid":"09a7efabceb3f5fe3ed15ee55a99d62425cc841d","tid":353780,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"諷刺嘅係<br />\n香港啲band多數支持政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ba5b1291dfd31eb5ca4ea8bb094ad1b3076d51","tid":353780,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"今天我&hellip;"},{"pid":"4d32b3f9fecb9d89648eebc2266bc2460d063707","tid":353780,"uid":43331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"Ha<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18da3e3c8f4a40187385585afc6efa8555ba19c7","tid":353780,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諷刺嘅係<br />\n香港啲band多數支持政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgHnMtfo_YY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwgHnMtfo_YY&d=G6m4a0XYGbAzLntwRX7pqNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fb81de27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgHnMtfo_YY</a>"},{"pid":"d6f47b9d116ea5839f50f1b815a0e9d7164a1d59","tid":353780,"uid":53765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"紅的不會理，理的不會紅"},{"pid":"93a5284b9cba129b5884161e272de59767ad50e2","tid":353780,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"所以中共好識玩<br />\n<br />\n直接控制樂隊既生計<br />\n用國企資本搵佢地接jobs<br />\n等佢地染紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩sub9 moment 咩五月天<br />\n咪又係接華為廣告 又怕得罪大陸封口唔講服貿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999ad2c842a1f43cf2de0e1471914c9cff94ce03","tid":353780,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"搖滾不容殺人政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bac6c33bb51b3be6efa0a9a8e943e1e025c59ed","tid":353780,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"共產就係相對平等既制度，就算有獨裁都比資本主義好。<br />\n<br />\n其實只係歐美資本家怕自己失去左人上人既地位，先抹黑共產主義。"},{"pid":"3b294c800db6c98c52e7cbfaa401ee7c92af1f6e","tid":353780,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共產就係相對平等既制度，就算有獨裁都比資本主義好。<br />\n<br />\n其實只係歐美資本家怕自己失去左人上人既地位，先抹黑共產主義。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係？？<br />\n有邊個'資本主義獨裁者'衰過老毛屎太淋？"},{"pid":"aa02f3daa1e922d2512701fd2b9e093a71250de2","tid":353780,"uid":35730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>共產就係相對平等既制度，就算有獨裁都比資本主義好。<br />\n<br />\n其實只係歐美資本家怕自己失去左人上人既地位，先抹黑共產主義。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係？？<br />\n有邊個'資本主義獨裁者'衰過老毛屎太淋？</blockquote><br />\n呢兩個偽社會主義既賤人就咪講啦，嚴格嚟講歐亞既社會主義政權都唔係社會主義"},{"pid":"93bb281b0b5be244ba987961cfb7541c44648b97","tid":353780,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:47:46.000Z","msg":"其實呢類果個時代呢堆嬉皮士，左翼解放果堆<br />\n好多人都當做自己黑歷史"},{"pid":"4c4b342f246b3b0301ec852b3543e85ffb6c108e","tid":353780,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1ba84c7b4ec4da88329b4831f635f8b595d204","tid":353780,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共產就係相對平等既制度，就算有獨裁都比資本主義好。<br />\n<br />\n其實只係歐美資本家怕自己失去左人上人既地位，先抹黑共產主義。</blockquote><br />\n人類天性唔適合共產<br />\n果然係低級公務員<br />\n做得五毛都係呢啲貨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb106391446c1599ef3dacc6ce151612e8b524dc","tid":353780,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"五毛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e2a685a398180f66a221a76768a06a2ecf521a","tid":353780,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0